dct_description_sm: Published at Washington D.C. January 1913 ; O.H. Tittmann, Superintendent.
Depths shown by soundings, dotted lines.
Submarine bells, storm warning displays, signs and abbreviations.
Shows low water areas, islands, coasts, waterways, cities and towns, lights.
